ote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"a11e213e-f190-8e43-15e2-2f13eac6eae0","name":"Note: New Task Form Submission"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp & Shape Task\n\nShapes the item: writes `taskId`, `receivedAt`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Payload Valid?","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"bd40724e-17b5-e8fa-35e5-992ab0d8a768","name":"Note: Stamp & Shape Task"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Payload Valid?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.taskId }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Prepare Approval Packet · ②→ Record Rejected Input","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"115ce4bb-412c-3b3e-b9e0-76bddc1f1e63","name":"Note: Payload Valid?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Record Rejected Input\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,1030],"id":"a3f761a1-17ee-cd5f-a67f-e91e4551f41e","name":"Note: Record Rejected Input"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Prepare Approval Packet\n\nShapes the item: writes `requestId`, `summary`, `requestedBy`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Request Approval via Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"7cfe3355-1133-40e1-1130-7887b3fe86a2","name":"Note: Prepare Approval Packet"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Request Approval via Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Hold for Decision · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,520],"id":"cf5db36c-7ee2-9ebb-cea4-57c791bd873b","name":"Note: Request Approval via Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Hold for Decision\n\nPauses the execution until the resume webhook is called — this is the approval/HITL gate.\n\nNext: Approved?","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,520],"id":"a85e52e2-b919-efdc-9c96-7ca3b4f1cb95","name":"Note: Hold for Decision"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Approved?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.body?.decision || $json.decision }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Execute Approved Action (API) · ②→ Record Decline + Notify Requester","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1614,520],"id":"cd4cee03-07db-c12d-8966-4691610aa5b1","name":"Note: Approved?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Execute Approved Action (API)\n\nPOST https://api.example.com/v1/tasks — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Join Decision Paths · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,280],"id":"411a1843-f3cf-69a5-f5af-ec7396ff72af","name":"Note: Execute Approved Action (API)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Record Decline + Notify Requester\n\ngmail — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Join Decision Paths · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2262,880],"id":"5620904d-3036-1b1c-4d67-eacdb9583cdb","name":"Note: Record Decline + Notify Requester"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Join Decision Paths\n\nRejoins 2 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Stamp Completion Time","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,520],"id":"74807548-a458-0e98-e365-2a4db9314bbf","name":"Note: Join Decision Paths"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Completion Time\n\nStamps `completedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Persist Run Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,520],"id":"bf28788f-24ac-a2e3-6535-724d4a717d59","name":"Note: Stamp Completion Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Persist Run Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Load Previous Snapshot","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4206,520],"id":"7f1af5ae-2033-b581-9bc1-095414d46ee0","name":"Note: Persist Run Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Load Previous Snapshot\n\ngoogleSheets — `read` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Compute Drift vs Snapshot · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4530,520],"id":"22923d25-5946-c852-ab78-37a7735f1efa","name":"Note: Load Previous Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Compute Drift vs Snapshot\n\nCustom JavaScript: Compare current metrics with the previous snapshot\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4854,520],"id":"9f843724-0cd4-868c-b0b5-cc91651a45f4","name":"Note: Compute Drift vs Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5178,520],"id":"66f0cade-f992-f283-1749-4ae87a5a7ba5","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Gmail · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5502,520],"id":"b6dcb9c0-de7f-76f8-caca-3355d223086e","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Gmail\n\ngmail — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5826,520],"id":"0a5fc9c7-5051-c0cc-ee15-ff12861be29b","name":"Note: Send Summary to Gmail"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5178,1540],"id":"2f2a45bd-6c0e-e7e7-a312-9828a3189017","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5502,1540],"id":"05f6c3ca-e340-ef95-4bd3-78e495bcc388","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5826,1540],"id":"6e4a0ddc-ba7d-5dff-03b8-fcc5bac53c42","name":"Note: Park in Dead-Letter Queue"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Approve expenses with Gmail and Google Drive without manual work\n\n**Pattern:** Approval Workflow · **Level:** Production · **Trigger:** Form\n\n## What it does\nApprove expenses with Gmail and Google Drive without manual work. It starts from a hosted form submission.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual task routing is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nNew Task Form Submission → Stamp & Shape Task → Payload Valid? → Prepare Approval Packet → Request Approval via Slack → Hold for Decision → Approved? → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to approval workflow without manual effort\n- Anyone automating task routing in software development\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Keeps your systems in sync\n- Scales without extra headcount\n- Standardizes the process every time\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; Google OAuth2; Google OAuth2 / service account; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"fbecc290-8a3f-0d9d-37e6-3978b3eef082","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Failures are also parked in a dead-letter queue for replay. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-260],"id":"83d72535-2382-1f27-4fcf-4db6d3916d5a","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## ⏱ Rate limiting\n\nWork is batched and spaced with Wait so provider quotas aren't tripped. If you hit 429s, lower the batch size or raise the wait — throughput drops, reliability rises.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-260],"id":"a380b90c-b723-ca31-b3e9-cbf907779c2f","name":"⏱ Rate limiting"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🙋 Human in the loop\n\nThe workflow pauses at the Wait node until a human posts a decision to the resume URL (included in the approval message). Approve → the action executes; anything else → recorded as declined. No timeout is set by default — add one under the Wait node's options if approvals go stale.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-260],"id":"ee56a251-b476-4e84-176c-ef760ff69ba8","name":"🙋 Human in the loop"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your task routing process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1030,-260],"id":"f9566426-c104-506e-c7f5-33d3a2586f44","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"New Task Form Submission":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp & Shape Task","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp & Shape Task":{"main":[[{"node":"Payload Valid?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Payload Valid?":{"main":[[{"node":"Prepare Approval Packet","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Record Rejected Input","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Prepare Approval Packet":{"main":[[{"node":"Request Approval via Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Request Approval via Slack":{"main":[[{"node":"Hold for Decision","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Hold for Decision":{"main":[[{"node":"Approved?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Approved?":{"main":[[{"node":"Execute Approved Action (API)","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Record Decline + Notify Requester","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Execute Approved Action (API)":{"main":[[{"node":"Join Decision Paths","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Record Decline + Notify Requester":{"main":[[{"node":"Join Decision Paths","type":"main","index":1}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Join Decision Paths":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Completion Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Completion Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Persist Run Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Persist Run Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Load Previous Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Load Previous Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Compute Drift vs Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Compute Drift vs Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Gmail","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Escalate Failure to Slack":{"main":[[{"node":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Gmail":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"1b42ed70-99b9-47c0-9977-2dc5b2d0220c","id":"FDX08440"}